  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A shield is made from wood or metal and is carried in one hand.</em></p>\n<p>Required strength = 17.</p>\n<p>Wielding a tower shield increases your Armor Class by 2.</p>\n<p><strong>Raise the Tower. </strong>When you are hit by an attack, you can use your reaction to <em>Raise the Tower</em>. Your AC is increased by +1 until the start of your next turn.</p>\n<p>A tower shield can be equipped or unequipped using an action on your turn.</p>\n<p>Whilst equipped, the wearer has disadvantage on Stealth checks and cannot take the Dash action.</p>\n<p> </p>",
